I'm sorry.

00:17:06.310 --> 00:17:07.400
Sit down.

00:17:07.400 --> 00:17:08.130
Okay.

00:17:11.110 --> 00:17:13.530
You have to finish it before someone comes in and sees us.

00:17:21.420 --> 00:17:23.400
What are you guys doing?

00:17:34.940 --> 00:17:39.570
Q, hold your audition number and face the camera.

00:17:39.640 --> 00:17:42.130
