00:17:42.130 --> 00:17:45.280
I guess both of you are familiar with each other since you two come from the same school.

00:18:00.550 --> 00:18:01.420
Thank you.

00:18:01.820 --> 00:18:05.550
If you're ready, Q can start a fight with X.

00:18:05.550 --> 00:18:10.480
The situation is like X takes a girl that you like out. You see them holding hands right in front of you.

00:18:10.480 --> 00:18:12.970
You can improvise. Okay?

00:18:13.000 --> 00:18:15.860
Of course. I'll give you my best shot.

00:18:20.800 --> 00:18:21.750
Hey!

00:18:22.600 --> 00:18:25.770
How dare you? You're so happy, huh?

00:18:27.200 --> 00:18:29.680
What are you talking about? I don't understand.

00:18:30.170 --> 00:18:32.540
I'm talking about...

00:18:32.860 --> 00:18:33.820
Mook.

00:18:34.170 --> 00:18:35.420
You took her out yesterday!

00:18:35.770 --> 00:18:39.260
You were holding hands while crossing the streets. Did you think no one would see you?

00:18:40.370 --> 00:18:41.950
Oh...

00:18:42.140 --> 00:18:43.840
Holding hands while crossing the streets?

00:18:43.840 --> 00:18:45.730
What's wrong with that?

00:18:45.730 --> 00:18:46.940
It's a normal thing to do.

00:18:47.840 --> 00:18:49.400
So, you finally admit it!

00:18:50.020 --> 00:18:52.710
Mook is my girlfriend!

00:18:53.370 --> 00:18:56.540
You're humiliating me by doing that.

00:18:57.150 --> 00:18:58.400
A person like you...

00:18:58.400 --> 00:19:00.400
I'll teach you a lesson!

00:19:01.340 --> 00:19:03.370
You like to assume things, don't you?

00:19:04.460 --> 00:19:07.400
You're so angry just because you saw me holding her hands.

00:19:08.400 --> 00:19:09.880
If you see me hug her

00:19:10.330 --> 00:19:12.330
or kiss her cheek,

00:19:12.330 --> 00:19:15.460
I guess you will...

00:19:18.000 --> 00:19:19.040
How dare you!

00:19:20.170 --> 00:19:21.640
You hugged and kissed her too?

00:19:21.640 --> 00:19:22.550
That's right.

00:19:22.820 --> 00:19:24.820
I did that right in front of her mother too.

00:19:24.820 --> 00:19:26.820
How could you do that in front of her mother?

00:19:31.530 --> 00:19:32.350
I could do that.

00:19:32.950 --> 00:19:34.200
Because...

00:19:34.400 --> 00:19:36.280
she's only three years old.

00:19:36.480 --> 00:19:38.530
I don't think you should have a girlfriend who's that young.

00:19:41.200 --> 00:19:42.440
Three years old?

00:19:44.540 --> 00:19:45.840
Er... Well...

00:19:45.840 --> 00:19:47.880
Okay, cut! That's enough.

00:19:47.880 --> 00:19:51.370
X, you're so good! I mean, both of you did well.

00:19:53.420 --> 00:19:54.660
Will you let go of my hand?

